    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing, the \"something new\" feels like a lie. it's just more of the same emptiness, just in a different shape. i feel like i've already reached the conclusion of my story. there isn't any more meaning to find, and trying to force it just feels... exhausting. like i'm just dragging a corpse around. doesn't it ever feel like some stories are just better off being finished?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
